	"title": "Board Games (Dice Dojo) (Edgewater)",
	"description": "board game meetup for chicago anime hangouts! hope to play some board games and have conversations about anime, and manga and more. just show up :D\n\ndice dojo has 1000+ games in their demo library. please support them if there\u2019s a game you like and want to purchase.\n\n**feel free to bring what you'd like to play!**\n\nschedule:\n6:00 pm: show up / checkin and get started with board games. their board game night starts at 5:00 and ends at 10:00 pm.\n\nname tags will be brought to indicate who's apart of the meetup.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\n\nhope to see you there!\n\\-\\-\\-\n\nThank you to the '[Chicagoland 20\u2019s and 30\u2019s Young Professionals](https://www.meetup.com/oak-park-west-suburbs-young-professionals/)' Meetup for advice on hosting board games. :D",
